name: G5 RARE PLODDING AQMRINE MNCHK
bio: Shalom! My name's G5 RARE PLODDING AQMRINE MNCHK. I once peed on Nelson Mandela's cat. They had it coming. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Stimpy. We can be friends, but keep the ultra purrsonal stuff to yourself, please.
